{"tid":1492868,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(中国滅佛)  觀音像被迫「腦袋開花」","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T10:38:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edf6d89ccc00a15dce5f8fd84cb97774c295d455","tid":1492868,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php2LQCte.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php2LQCte.jpg&h=d28bfd56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖翻攝自《寒冬》官網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌昨刊文表示，位於遼寧省的大河貝生態息園墓園內，有座四面觀音像被迫「腦袋開花」，駿龍泉墓園一尊地藏王菩薩被大理石板包圍，村民怒批以前多好看，現在「像個碑似的！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpydiYB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpydiYB4.jpg&h=f0708f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n   （圖翻攝自《寒冬》官網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》報導，遼寧省鐵嶺市鐵嶺縣曾警告當地墓園不准有露天佛像，5月大河貝生態息園墓園為防止佛像被拆，只好替高約20公尺的四面觀音像「整容」，耗時逾3個月把頭部點綴成「荷花形狀」。員工無奈回應，即便曉得四不像、看了彆扭，但不這麼做就得全拆。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，該縣駿龍泉墓園另有一尊10多公尺高的地藏王菩薩，接連兩次分別被以鐵皮封住、大理石板包圍，第一次用鐵皮時，上頭還寫著二十四孝，但官員不滿意，才有第二次。村民見狀直呼，「佛露在外面多好看啊！現在整那個玩意，像個碑似的」。<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，報導提到，坐落於山西省的國家4A級旅遊景區藏山，區內的蓮花寺原有尊16公尺高的觀音像，但6月下旬被強拆，政府對外則宣稱「施工改造」，並派人看守。工作人員透露，「他們（政府）說旅遊區不是拜佛的地方，不允許有菩薩像存在」。<br />\n<br />\n報導提及，不過，似非所有官員都贊成強拆佛像，就有知情人士提到，「現在是習近平掌權，他說要整治佛教，誰敢擰著幹！」若一個不注意官員恐「就地免職」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，報導引述，6月玄龍寺一尊15公尺高的菩薩像也難逃被強拆命運，目擊者指出，當時八旬住持數度上前攔阻卻直接被抬走。知情者說，該寺住持積極響應官方政策，不過仍遭到打壓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2889755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2889755&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41MmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=c45bec90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2889755&h=19038608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2889755</a>"},{"pid":"a589a54dd0caba45dd5439d195fa8ddbaf1ef539","tid":1492868,"uid":63423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"貼毛魔保平安，百毒不侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46535c9fa416a874b15387e1474eed8904929e73","tid":1492868,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"呢家上面天災人禍，係咪天譴"},{"pid":"5feaf459d66cc971eb02cc7cbf97c648ccc4f6e4","tid":1492868,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46535c9fa416a874b15387e1474eed8904929e73","tid":1492868,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"呢家上面天災人禍，係咪天譴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">皇</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a8ef0c34ab76ad0eb161172f3ae6487212aa5fa","tid":1492868,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939aedcb41ec8d361c17f03ed1d3c3a5f7811006","tid":1492868,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5feaf459d66cc971eb02cc7cbf97c648ccc4f6e4","tid":1492868,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46535c9fa416a874b15387e1474eed8904929e73","tid":1492868,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"呢家上面天災人禍，係咪天譴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">皇</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:16:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong>天</strong></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"41cd796b048a0992aeb7c873ae9bad9d05c14399","tid":1492868,"uid":159184,"like":0,"dislik